---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../layouts/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Provencraft Community">
    <main
        class="grid min-h-full place-items-center px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8 bg-[#001D3D]"
    >
        <div id="center" class="text-center text-white">
            <!-- </div> -->
            <div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
                <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
                    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
                        <p
                            class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl"
                        >
                            What's in it for me?
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8">
                            Here is the list of awesome reasons for you to join
                            our community to unlock new adventures and
                            opportunities
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl"
                    >
                        <dl
                            class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-y-16 text-left"
                        >
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    Personal and professional growth
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    You'll have access to various resources and
                                    opportunities that will help you develop
                                    your skills, knowledge, and experience.
                                    Whether through workshops, events,
                                    mentorship, or collaboration, you'll be able
                                    to grow personally and professionally.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    Opportunities to learn and explore
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    Our community is a space to try new things and explore new ideas. We encourage our members to take risks, think outside the box, and learn from one another. You'll have access to a wealth of knowledge and resources to help you expand your horizons and discover new passions.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    A supportive and inclusive environment
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    One of the most significant benefits is the sense of belonging and support you'll feel. We prioritize creating a safe and inclusive space where everyone feels welcome and valued. You'll be able to connect with like-minded individuals who share your interests and goals.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    Develop your personal brand
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    Joining the community and sharing your knowledge and expertise can help you develop a personal brand by establishing yourself as a thought leader, increasing your visibility, building trust and credibility, and leading to new opportunities.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    Leadership and mentorship opportunities
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    If you are a seasoned professional, you likely have much to offer regarding leadership and mentorship. You can mentor younger members, lead community projects, or even start your venture.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative pl-16">
                                <dt
                                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-7"
                                >
                                    Networking opportunities
                                </dt>
                                <dd
                                    class="mt-2 text-base leading-7"
                                >
                                    By joining this community, you'll have the chance to connect with other professionals in your field, share your expertise, and learn from others. You may even meet potential collaborators or partners for future projects.
                                </dd>
                            </div>
                            <Card title="Networking opportunities" description="By joining this community, you'll have the chance to connect with other professionals in your field, share your expertise, and learn from others. You may even meet potential collaborators or partners for future projects.">
                            </Card>
                        </dl>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
